experiment ReimeiESR
instrument ESR
start 2008 10 31 0700
end 2008 10 31 1000
status R
description Reimei-ESR coordinated observations of ion upflows/polar wind
contact M. Hirahara
phone +81-3-5841-4582
email hirahara@eps.s.u-tokyo.ac.jp
fax +81-3-5841-8321
operator Y. Ogawa from Tromso site
submitter Yasunobu Ogawa (yogawa@nipr.ac.jp)
resources NI(3)
notes
This is a comparative study of velocity distributions 
of precipitating electrons and outflowing ions with 
the ionospheric ion upflows/polar wind using the Reimei 
satellite and ESR.
Reimei will pass over Svalbard at about 07:43 and
09:19 UT on October 31.
